#    https://github.com/p-ranav/argparse (the p-ranav/argparse library)
#
#  Authored by Ed Asriyan (ed-asriyan/lottie-converter).  1021 GH stars.
#  Single-binary Lottie animation converter — reads .json/.lottie/.tgs
#  files and produces a sequence of PNG frames.  The lottie-converter
#  project also ships shell wrappers (lottie_to_apng.sh / lottie_to_gif.sh
#  / lottie_to_webp.sh / lottie_to_webm.sh) that post-process these PNG
#  frames into animated formats via ffmpeg.  Sister tools: rlottie
#  (Samsung's Lottie renderer used by this project under the hood),
#  Adobe After Effects (creates Lottie animations).
