#  Dup-skipped neighbors during hunt (smaller surface or unrelated):
#    - drakvuf-sandbox (CERT-Polska — uses p-ranav/argparse for IPT
#      analyzer; HOLD for future round)
#    - UStore (unum-cloud — uses p-ranav/argparse but DB-internal tools)
